{"tid":1241420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失敗主義，心灰意冷，袋住先，兩個禮拜好攰…","createTime":"2019-06-18T16:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:35:17.000Z","uid":123497,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41a1b8040b2014c15620a343eba51679cc6f688d","tid":1241420,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"共產黨表面上完美嘅計劃點都會有缺口<br />\n我哋依家漫無目的<br />\n全部都係因為你哋仲未睇到缺口<br />\n<br />\n佢哋現時嘅缺口喺：記者會自打嘴巴，令建制支持者好混亂<br />\n<br />\n參考返上兩個禮拜<br />\n我哋軟硬兼施<br />\n只為一個目的<br />\n就係撤回惡法<br />\n<br />\n基於上述前設<br />\n我認為應該只攻一至兩個point<br />\n唔好一次過叫五個訴求<br />\n<br />\n而叫邊個訴求最好呢？<br />\n我希望你哋明白<br />\n叫撤回惡法同釋放被捕人士呢兩個point已經出現疲態<br />\n正正就係因為林鄭半撤回同半放人<br />\n而係建制同警犬士氣咁差既情況下<br />\n應該淨係針爆警隊所做嘅暴力行為同警權過大問題<br />\n俾最大既壓力班狗/監狗會<br />\n咁先為上策"},{"pid":"f9e2e70fa5b443bd2940b894d12f66551ab7bf8e","tid":1241420,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"救義士！"},{"pid":"6a449213bfcdb50b57668ee5c44be5cc69664266","tid":1241420,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e2e70fa5b443bd2940b894d12f66551ab7bf8e","tid":1241420,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"救義士！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"我明要救<br />\n但共狗好撚識玩政治 一定唔會放晒<br />\n我哋要贏一定要記住我哋宗旨"},{"pid":"8520a6985e9fa8d80ad00961a25233642c88bc24","tid":1241420,"uid":123497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:50:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9890c16901f9cc935e870d2c2adcf4fdaded8d88","tid":1241420,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"f4d43f45512aaf523aa9aa90ce990a66f0ee1d32","tid":1241420,"uid":120393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:53:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b901fefee7ca80496dad489949e06c3ef8b3bcbc","tid":1241420,"uid":263365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime